        ./config.sh --unattended --url "https://$GITHUB_DOMAIN/$OWNER/$REPO" --token "$RUNNER_TOKEN" --ephemeral --work _work --labels "$RUNNER_LABEL" --disableupdate --name "$RUNNER_NAME" && 
        ./run.sh &&
        STATUS=$(grep -Phors "finish job request for job [0-9a-f\-]+ with result: \K.*" _diag/ | tail -n1) &&
        [ -n "$STATUS" ] && echo CDKGHA JOB DONE "$RUNNER_LABEL" "$STATUS"
containerDefinitions.name: runner

securityGroupEgress.description: Allow all outbound traffic by default

aws:cdk:cloudformation:props.filterPattern: [..., marker = "CDKGHA", job = "JOB", done = "DONE", labels, status = "Succeeded" || status = "SucceededWithIssues" || status = "Failed" || status = "Canceled" || status = "Skipped" || status = "Abandoned"]
